Package: honcho-inspector-backend
Version: 0.1.0-SNAPSHOT
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: cloudBSD <admin@cloudbsd.org>
Depends: openjdk-25-jre-headless | java25-runtime-headless | default-jre-headless (>= 21), adduser
Recommends: sqlite3
Description: Honcho Inspector backend
 Multi-user admin surface for Honcho. Provides a REST API for
 browsing, editing, and managing Honcho workspaces. Runs as an
 unprivileged system user on loopback (127.0.0.1:8080) and is
 intended to be fronted by a reverse proxy.
